Randgold Resources First-Quarter Profit More Than Doubles to $41.5 Million

-- B y   A m a n d a   J o r d a n
-- 
2011-05-05T06:00:16Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-05/randgold-resources-first-quarter-profit-more-than-doubles-to-41-5-million.html
Randgold Resources Ltd. (RRS) , a miner of
the metal in  Africa , said net income more than doubled to $41.5
million in the first quarter from $18.7 million a year earlier.  Gold production climbed to 139,403 ounces from 112,663
ounces, the  Jersey , Channel Islands-based company said today in
a statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Amanda Jordan in London at 
